#
# 2. Download private key (.pem file)
#    Convert to single line with \n:
#    cat private-key.pem | sed ':a;N;$!ba;s/\n/\\n/g'
#
# 3. Setup ngrok (for development):
#    ngrok http 8000
#    Copy HTTPS URL to GITHUB_WEBHOOK_URL
#
# 4. Update GitHub App webhook URL with ngrok URL
#
# 5. Install dependencies:
#    pip install PyJWT cryptography
#
# 6. Run migrations:
#    python manage.py makemigrations
#    python manage.py migrate
#
# 7. Start server:
#    python manage.py runserver
#
# 8. Connect app from frontend:
